__TOC__

** Face to face meet up on Thursday 1st of October with <nowiki>[[http://www.linux.ie/|ILUG]]</nowiki> in the <nowiki>[[http://www.thelongstone.com|Longstone]]</nowiki>. 

* The loco held a <nowiki>[[https://wiki.ubuntu.com/IrishTeam/GlobalJam09|Global Jam]]</nowiki> on the Saturday, the 3rd of October in <nowiki>[[http://www.tog.ie/|TOG]]</nowiki>.

* Regular <nowiki>[[https://wiki.ubuntu.com/IrishTeam/IRCMeetings/2009-10-14|Monthly IRC Meeting]]</nowiki> was held at 8pm Irish time on Wednesday 14th October 2009.

* The loco held a Karmic Koala release party on Saturday 31st October. First we had some food in <nowiki>[[http://www.jimmychungs.com/locate/loc_dublin.htm|Jimmy Chungs]]</nowiki> and then onto the <nowiki>[[http://www.handelshoteltemplebar.com/bar.html|Karma]]</nowiki> for drinks. A write up about the event can be found <nowiki>[[http://www.lczajkowski.com/2009/11/01/karmic-koala-in-karma-dublin/|here]]</nowiki> and some <nowiki>[[http://pix.ie/czajkowski/album/359447|photos]]</nowiki>.
